Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.50,0:23:37.97,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}我对运气
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:43.23,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}无所指望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.51,0:23:47.88,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}对这胸中的光荣的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.94,0:23:51.86,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}沉重的负担
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.05,0:23:55.40,ed_chi,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}{\be1}有所准备
